JOHN BUSH:   Tough golf course.
RICKIE FOWLER:   Yeah.   I mean, it is a tough golf course if you put yourself in the wrong position.   Today the wind kind of laid down a little bit towards the second half.
Jordan got off to a good start it looked like.   It wasn't playing easy early on.   Definitely some tough holes out here.   Looks like he took advantage of getting some on those holes and some of the easier ones.
I'm definitely happy with the start. 

